nodes.title: Prompt 1
widgets_values: A woman with vibrant teal hair styled in a thick braid, adorned with geometric tattoos on her chest and arms, leans forward with eyes closed in submission. Her left hand rests gently against the man’s thigh while her right arm is restrained by silver handcuffs dangling from a chain. The man, whose torso is visible with tribal markings on his shoulder and forearm, holds her head tenderly with one hand as he penetrates her mouth. Soft sunlight filters through sheer curtains behind them, casting warm highlights across their skin and creating gentle shadows in the room’s corners. A wooden countertop sits blurred in the background with a small bottle resting beside it. Her piercing glints subtly under the light, adding to the sensual atmosphere of the intimate moment captured.

nodes.title: Prompt 4
widgets_values: The final frame captures the woman leaning back just enough to look directly into his eyes as he withdraws slowly from her mouth. Her expression shifts from intense concentration to quiet contentment, a soft smile playing at her lips despite the restraint on her arm. The handcuffs catch the light as they swing gently with her motion, adding a subtle metallic echo to the scene. Sunlight bathes their skin in golden tones, creating a warm glow that contrasts with the darker elements of the room behind them. Her hair cascades over one shoulder like liquid teal silk, catching every ray of light filtering through the window. The image ends on this tender moment — intimate, sensual, and deeply connected.

nodes.title: Prompt 3
widgets_values: The camera slowly zooms out to reveal more of the room’s decor — dark wood cabinetry lining one wall and a glimpse of an ornate mirror reflecting part of their forms. The woman's eyes flutter open briefly, meeting his gaze before closing again in surrender. Her breath hitches softly as she continues to take him deeper into her mouth, her movements becoming more fluid and controlled. The man’s grip on her head tightens slightly for a moment before loosening, allowing her to adjust her angle without breaking rhythm. Shadows stretch across the floorboards beneath them, elongating with each passing second.
